Hub - packet coming in a port will be sent out to all other ports
Bridge - intelligent forwarding decision by learning MACs, slow software based
Switch - Fast as Hub + Intelligent as Bridge
  ASIC (Application Specific Integrated Circuitry) - chip that converts software function of a bridge into hardware function for high speed
  Layer 2 - CAM (Content Accessible Memory) table
  Layer 3 - built-in routing
Router - divides broadcast domain, allows unicast between different networks
Firewall
  Transparent
  Routed
  
